        "message": "Vonage API Key detected in variable assignment. Vonage API Keys are public identifiers used alongside API Secrets to authenticate API requests. While API Keys are less sensitive than secrets, exposing them can reveal service usage patterns and should be protected. Always pair with secure API Secret storage and use environment variables for configuration.",
